            <title><![CDATA[【[干饭人]#夫妻先后患癌原因就在饭桌上# 】 📢专家提醒：吃饭要适量，不要吃得过饱！特别是晚上，吃得过饱，容易引起胃食管反流。长期如此，在胃酸的刺激下，...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[干饭人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E5%85%88%E5%90%8E%E6%82%A3%E7%99%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E5%B0%B1%E5%9C%A8%E9%A5%AD%E6%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E5%85%88%E5%90%8E%E6%82%A3%E7%99%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E5%B0%B1%E5%9C%A8%E9%A5%AD%E6%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#夫妻先后患癌原因就在饭桌上#</span></a> 】 📢专家提醒：吃饭要适量，不要吃得过饱！特别是晚上，吃得过饱，容易引起胃食管反流。长期如此，在胃酸的刺激下，会增加食管癌变的几率。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4992363152474143" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hm0e3o58h9j21hc0u0n23.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/JGkzO81ilx08bTAdXCso01041200EK7B0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705943799&amp;ssig=3kfleekt4V&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/BptSy9Fhlx08bTAcx0z601041200hOtW0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705943799&amp;ssig=EjnGWEKS0%2F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/pXTwEgb1lx08bTAc3eiQ01041200aDNJ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705943799&amp;ssig=0SEHI5SDHk&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4992363152474143" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
